"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqifG4s.jpg&h=2c8544c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煮既時候注意下火喉應該就冇咩問題，最怕個底黑哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果想同廚師或者我瘋狂傾計，就可以訂閱埋我地既facebook 同ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/captopuskitchen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcaptopuskitchen&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=e51e1baa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/captopuskitchen</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/catopuskitchen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcatopuskitchen%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=fda31c3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/catopuskitchen/</a>"},{"pid":"ead7793e48f62480b29284c087e54423234d6cbb","tid":2233884,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2e217e17169d7bdc1adce13d5c9b61880bb54653","tid":2233884,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"臘腸煲仔飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f155bbe783158d4cc2b8dd7169332471d7c7ccce","tid":2233884,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ead7793e48f62480b29284c087e54423234d6cbb","tid":2233884,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:49:06.000Z","msg":"我下次又1你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b796b2c2cddf8d203b7a0e40bb5f2f64675